OL,3,CWhisky family lose #1.6 billion but
OL,4,Cstill top Channel Islands' rich list
OL,6,FThe wealthiest person in the Channel
OL,7,FIslands has been named in The Sunday
OL,8,FTimes Rich List for 2026.
OL,10,FDespite being down around #1.6
OL,11,Fbillion, the owner of spirits company
OL,12,FWilliam Grant & Sons, Jersey's Glenn
OL,13,FGordon and his family, top the list
OL,14,Fwith a fortune of around #4.75 billion.
OL,16,FHe is one of the 14 islanders who have
OL,17,Fbeen named among the richest 350
OL,18,Fpeople in the UK, who live in Jersey
OL,19,For Guernsey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
