CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778955067
OL,3,CWhisky family lose #1.6 billion but
OL,4,Cstill top Channel Islands' rich list
OL,6,FRobert Watts, compiler of the Sunday
OL,7,FTimes Rich List, explains why the
OL,8,FChannel Islands may be appealing. He
OL,9,Fsays: "Obviously, it is a wonderful
OL,10,Fplace to live, it has a nicer climate
OL,11,Fthan the UK, wonderful beaches and
OL,12,Fpace of life, but tax is a big part of
OL,13,Fit, there is no doubt about it.
OL,15,F"Low income tax rates and critically
OL,16,Fthe zero capital gains tax, and zero
OL,17,Finheritance tax."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778955067
OL,3,CWhisky family lose #1.6 billion but
OL,4,Cstill top Channel Islands' rich list
OL,6,FHe adds: "A lot of these places which
OL,7,Fthe super rich are going to are a trek
OL,8,Faway - Monaco, Switzerland, whereas
OL,9,Fyou can wake up in Jersey or Guernsey
OL,10,Fand make it to London for a mid-
OL,11,Fmorning meeting and continue to work
OL,12,Ffrom there.
OL,14,F"So the Channel Islands really do have
OL,15,Fa special advantage over some islands."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
