CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778955067
OL,3,CWhisky family lose #1.6 billion but
OL,4,Cstill top Channel Islands' rich list
OL,6,FHowever, Robert points out that giving
OL,7,Fresidency to the super-rich can be a
OL,8,Fdivisive subject: "Some people think
OL,9,Fit's great, they bring their money,
OL,10,Fthey bring their spending. Others take
OL,11,Fthe other view: 'What does the island
OL,12,Freally get out of these people? Should
OL,13,Fwe get more out of them via tax?'
OL,15,F"So whether having the super-rich here
OL,16,Fis something to be proud of still
OL,17,Fdivides opinion."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
